query:
SELECT r.id, r.status, r.totalValue, o.title as outdoor_name, rb.biweekId, rb.status as biweek_status, b.biweekNumber
FROM reservations r
JOIN outdoors o ON r.outdoorId = o.id
LEFT JOIN reservation_biweeks rb ON r.id = rb.reservationId
LEFT JOIN biweeks b ON rb.biweekId = b.id
WHERE o.title LIKE '%Fepasa%'
ORDER BY r.id DESC, b.biweekNumber ASC
LIMIT 50;
